- id
- title
- slug
- price
- description
- image_path
- page_count
- published_date
- isbn
- created_at
- updated_at

BookItem
- id
- book_id
- price
- inventory_code
- reserved_at (nullable)
- order_id (nullable)
- created_at
- updated_at

book_category
- id
- book_id
- category_id
- created_at
- updated_at

Category
- id
